      <title>特朗普关税风险引发伦敦黄金市场混乱追逐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/trump-tariff-risks-are-fueling-a-chaotic-hunt-for-gold-in-london</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普实施普遍进口关税的风险正在引发全球黄金市场的新一轮动荡，备受关注的黄金需求晴雨表在伦敦达到了历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/trump-tariff-risks-are-fueling-a-chaotic-hunt-for-gold-in-london</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 14:46:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛向首席执行官所罗门提供 8000 万美元留任，薪酬提高 26%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/goldman-hands-80-million-retention-awards-to-solomon-waldron</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 向两名高管分别颁发了价值 8,000 万美元的留任奖金，并启动了一项计划，为其高管提供私募股权基金所获的部分附带收益，以期在薪酬方面与顶级另类资产管理公司展开竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/goldman-hands-80-million-retention-awards-to-solomon-waldron</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 14:18:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
